1
00:00:06,298 --> 00:00:08,850
Is there no honorable man within our forces?

2
00:00:08,850 --> 00:00:10,650
Yang Zhi, the Blue-faced Beast.

3
00:00:10,650 --> 00:00:12,020
Now that is a good tale.

4
00:00:12,020 --> 00:00:13,150
I must decline.

5
00:00:13,150 --> 00:00:16,810
I do not wish to associate
with Liangshan Marsh any further.

6
00:00:16,810 --> 00:00:18,410
Why do something so foolish?

7
00:00:18,410 --> 00:00:21,530
To help you escape, An Dao Quan.

8
00:00:21,530 --> 00:00:24,650
I would never lose.

9
00:00:24,650 --> 00:00:28,320
I, Lin Chong the Panther Head,
will now be breaking free!

10
00:00:28,320 --> 00:00:32,190
You will have Zhu Gui repay the favor
by allowing us to see Wang Lun?

11
00:00:32,190 --> 00:00:35,730
I will take you to my comrades!

12
00:00:35,730 --> 00:00:41,255
This invisible enemy
is aware of our presence.

13
00:00:41,255 --> 00:00:45,485
Lin Chong has returned.

14
00:01:21,750 --> 00:01:24,280
[Wanted: Lin Chong]
[Episode 4]

15
00:01:34,946 --> 00:01:37,186
You have done well to return to us.

16
00:01:39,250 --> 00:01:41,680
- Now eat your fill.
- I shall.

17
00:01:43,940 --> 00:01:48,760
Posters of you cover the village boards.

18
00:01:58,550 --> 00:02:03,660
I see I am now wanted across the nation.

19
00:02:07,705 --> 00:02:09,980
How is Bai Sheng?

20
00:02:09,980 --> 00:02:12,350
Wu Yong is looking after him.

21
00:02:12,350 --> 00:02:15,965
Lin Chong, you are just as battered.

22
00:02:15,965 --> 00:02:19,388
You must first worry about yourself, no?

23
00:02:19,388 --> 00:02:22,543
Food has cured me of my ailments.

24
00:02:22,543 --> 00:02:24,083
Is that so?

25
00:02:25,860 --> 00:02:31,960
Now, how shall we acquire the fortress
within Liangshan Marsh?

26
00:02:32,675 --> 00:02:34,290
My plan remains unchanged.

27
00:02:34,290 --> 00:02:38,000
It is an impregnable castle.

28
00:02:38,635 --> 00:02:42,560
We cannot charge in with a frontal assault.

29
00:02:42,560 --> 00:02:49,335
I do not wish to lose an ally
over a reckless battle.

30
00:02:49,335 --> 00:02:51,785
That is how I feel.

31
00:03:00,264 --> 00:03:06,520
Sir Song Jiang, give the order,
and I shall sneak in.

32
00:03:06,520 --> 00:03:08,256
Lin Chong...

33
00:03:08,256 --> 00:03:09,971
Do not worry for me.

34
00:03:09,971 --> 00:03:11,931
As I rest...

35
00:03:13,335 --> 00:03:16,100
I am only haunted by the past.

36
00:03:16,100 --> 00:03:18,660
I heard of Zhang Lan's fate.

37
00:03:21,780 --> 00:03:27,000
<i>Love does not need a reason, my dear.</i>

38
00:03:29,980 --> 00:03:31,640
Lin Chong.

39
00:03:33,020 --> 00:03:35,410
Do you wish to die?

40
00:03:38,937 --> 00:03:41,527
I cannot die.

41
00:03:42,980 --> 00:03:45,976
You have finally returned.

42
00:03:45,976 --> 00:03:48,831
I will not send you to your death again.

43
00:03:52,150 --> 00:03:54,330
I shall be fine, sir.

44
00:03:56,225 --> 00:03:59,900
Say, who is this?

45
00:03:59,900 --> 00:04:01,905
That is Xue Yong.
[Xue Yong, Apothecary]

46
00:04:01,905 --> 00:04:06,825
He concocts effective medicines.
Almost none can match his skills.

47
00:04:07,950 --> 00:04:11,290
A renowned doctor and apothecary?
What a pair.

48
00:04:13,425 --> 00:04:16,816
- What are you doing?
- Your treatment requires a do-over.

49
00:04:16,816 --> 00:04:20,686
Even spit would prove more effective
than this "salve".

50
00:04:22,125 --> 00:04:24,400
Where did you find this man?

51
00:04:24,400 --> 00:04:26,060
I sent Lu Zhi Shen to him.

52
00:04:26,060 --> 00:04:29,400
He carried my message across the land.

53
00:04:29,400 --> 00:04:32,900
Xue Yong is the best ally I could ask for.

54
00:04:32,900 --> 00:04:35,850
We will cure many illnesses together.

55
00:04:35,850 --> 00:04:38,020
Lu Zhi Shen.

56
00:04:38,020 --> 00:04:42,020
A man who, for one reason or another,

57
00:04:42,020 --> 00:04:44,255
excels at running into capable men,

58
00:04:44,255 --> 00:04:49,485
and ultimately enamors them.

59
00:05:19,710 --> 00:05:21,790
You wield a good sword there.

60
00:05:23,030 --> 00:05:29,580
You can tell,
without me unsheathing the sword?

61
00:05:30,225 --> 00:05:35,690
Just as I can tell
a person's status from their garbs.

62
00:05:35,690 --> 00:05:40,260
The might of your blade
is obvious from a glance.

63
00:05:43,590 --> 00:05:48,580
The Splitting Hairs Blade.
It is an ancestral sword of mine.

64
00:05:49,850 --> 00:05:55,250
Yet you stare at a noble blade
with much sadness. Why?

65
00:06:04,105 --> 00:06:06,910
What is with this report?

66
00:06:06,910 --> 00:06:08,685
I have merely written the truth, sir.

67
00:06:08,685 --> 00:06:11,180
"Bandits"!

68
00:06:11,180 --> 00:06:16,825
We did not execute "villagers" in that town.

69
00:06:16,825 --> 00:06:18,995
We executed "bandits". Understand?

70
00:06:32,130 --> 00:06:34,000
Write!

71
00:06:35,495 --> 00:06:37,650
Write, and bring your revisions here!

72
00:06:37,650 --> 00:06:43,230
Executing innocent villagers,
under the guise of killing bandits.

73
00:06:43,230 --> 00:06:45,375
Gao Qiu has gone mad.

74
00:06:45,375 --> 00:06:51,435
He is venting his frustrations
after failing to assassinate Lin Chong.

75
00:06:52,156 --> 00:06:54,596
He has yet to be found?

76
00:06:56,125 --> 00:06:58,980
Yes. We must simply continue our search.

77
00:06:58,980 --> 00:07:03,090
The strongest spearman now roams free,

78
00:07:03,090 --> 00:07:05,717
while we are left with a foolish general.

79
00:07:05,717 --> 00:07:10,437
Nothing is more frightening
than a fool with power.

80
00:07:11,335 --> 00:07:15,110
It makes their next moves unpredictable.

81
00:07:15,110 --> 00:07:17,060
Agreed.

82
00:07:20,270 --> 00:07:22,120
Shall we kill him?

83
00:07:24,075 --> 00:07:27,810
We must not be suspected of treason.

84
00:07:27,810 --> 00:07:29,450
Then what to do?

85
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:35,740
We shall simply allow him
to kick his ball as he pleases.

86
00:07:39,455 --> 00:07:44,350
Why are you so stubborn?

87
00:07:44,350 --> 00:07:46,980
I fight the battles I am ordered to.

88
00:07:46,980 --> 00:07:48,940
That is the duty of a soldier.

89
00:07:48,940 --> 00:07:51,790
I need not consider anything else.

90
00:07:51,790 --> 00:07:56,220
You have the talent to command an army.

91
00:07:56,220 --> 00:07:58,810
You are no ordinary foot soldier.

92
00:07:58,810 --> 00:08:01,980
How can you tell? We have only just met.

93
00:08:01,980 --> 00:08:04,190
I have spoken to many men in my life.

94
00:08:04,190 --> 00:08:06,445
I can tell these things.

95
00:08:06,445 --> 00:08:10,585
Is this not true, ancestor of Yang Ye?

96
00:08:12,055 --> 00:08:15,350
Indeed. I now carry the will of my ancestors.

97
00:08:15,350 --> 00:08:19,895
I report all wrongdoings
to the Imperial Guard, and...

98
00:08:19,895 --> 00:08:24,855
Hah! Gao Qiu will cover up any such reports.

99
00:08:26,790 --> 00:08:31,310
How do you know of the inner workings
of the Imperial Guard?

100
00:08:31,310 --> 00:08:33,175
I am a wandering monk.

101
00:08:33,175 --> 00:08:36,065
Rumors make their way to my ears.

102
00:08:44,415 --> 00:08:47,330
I had heard of a suspicious, bald monk,

103
00:08:47,330 --> 00:08:51,050
who hoped to throw our country into disarray.

104
00:08:54,015 --> 00:08:58,250
Most bald folk are suspicious.

105
00:08:58,250 --> 00:09:01,660
You cannot suspect us all.

106
00:09:03,270 --> 00:09:06,200
Who are these "men" you have met with?

107
00:09:07,589 --> 00:09:12,414
One was a man named Wang Jin.
Another, Lin Chong.

108
00:09:12,414 --> 00:09:15,224
They are both criminals.

109
00:09:16,557 --> 00:09:19,320
The real criminals are the Imperial Guard.

110
00:09:19,320 --> 00:09:21,520
What?

111
00:09:21,520 --> 00:09:26,810
Gao Qiu ordered a strike
on a tribe of bandits.

112
00:09:26,810 --> 00:09:28,980
Did you hear of this?

113
00:09:28,980 --> 00:09:30,950
Of course.

114
00:09:30,950 --> 00:09:33,511
It was an ordinary village
that Gao Qiu had attacked.

115
00:09:33,511 --> 00:09:36,281
There were no bandits in sight.

116
00:09:36,925 --> 00:09:41,220
I hear they took the heads
of several hundred thieves.

117
00:09:41,220 --> 00:09:46,220
No. He slaughtered innocent citizens.

118
00:09:46,915 --> 00:09:49,560
Gao Qiu, failing to catch any bandits,

119
00:09:49,560 --> 00:09:55,465
killed ordinary folk
to embellish his accomplishments.

120
00:09:55,465 --> 00:09:57,900
That cannot be.

121
00:09:57,900 --> 00:10:01,135
Would you have taken part in the slaughter?

122
00:10:01,135 --> 00:10:05,395
You, a soldier who merely follows orders.

123
00:10:06,625 --> 00:10:09,560
This is why our people suffer.

124
00:10:09,560 --> 00:10:13,860
Our soldiers fight,
without thinking for themselves.

125
00:10:13,860 --> 00:10:17,210
This country ought to...

126
00:10:29,785 --> 00:10:33,520
Apologies. I got a little heated.

127
00:10:33,520 --> 00:10:36,830
Here, have a drink.

128
00:10:41,165 --> 00:10:43,360
I must decline.

129
00:10:43,360 --> 00:10:45,620
You make this alcohol taste bitter.

130
00:10:46,688 --> 00:10:50,850
There are two reasons
why alcohol would taste bitter.

131
00:10:50,850 --> 00:10:53,755
One, is that your body cries for help.

132
00:10:53,755 --> 00:10:57,565
The other, is that your heart cries for help.

133
00:10:59,965 --> 00:11:06,280
You say this "Yang Zhi"
is more than a spoiled coward?

134
00:11:06,280 --> 00:11:07,596
I believe so.

135
00:11:07,596 --> 00:11:12,480
He commands ten men
like an army of a hundred,

136
00:11:12,480 --> 00:11:18,620
and a hundred men like an army of ten.

137
00:11:19,495 --> 00:11:24,510
If we allowed him an army of 10,000,

138
00:11:24,510 --> 00:11:28,431
what would he be capable of?

139
00:11:28,431 --> 00:11:30,661
That is what Lu Zhi Shen writes.

140
00:11:35,890 --> 00:11:37,620
What is it, my friend?

141
00:11:40,090 --> 00:11:44,620
I want this man for ourselves.

142
00:11:47,295 --> 00:11:50,190
Once we have acquired our fortress,

143
00:11:50,190 --> 00:11:55,460
we will need a general to command an army.

144
00:11:57,495 --> 00:12:02,810
But I believe Yang Zhi will not fold easily.

145
00:12:02,810 --> 00:12:05,910
Though that is another fine trait of his.

146
00:12:07,400 --> 00:12:11,660
He will find his way here.

147
00:12:13,817 --> 00:12:20,190
All who feel betrayed by the Imperial Guard

148
00:12:20,190 --> 00:12:23,300
will eventually wash up to our shores.

149
00:12:27,450 --> 00:12:31,920
We must acquire that fortress
as soon as possible.

150
00:12:35,190 --> 00:12:36,790
I've got a catch!

151
00:12:40,196 --> 00:12:42,916
After we acquire the fortress,

152
00:12:43,680 --> 00:12:46,100
we shall gather an army.

153
00:12:46,100 --> 00:12:49,730
We will have men like Yang Zhi
and Lin Chong be our generals,

154
00:12:49,730 --> 00:12:52,170
and best this country, once and for all.

155
00:12:52,925 --> 00:12:54,506
Sounds like a fine dream.

156
00:12:54,506 --> 00:12:58,106
It is no dream. It is our end goal.

157
00:13:02,990 --> 00:13:04,960
This is a big one.

158
00:13:08,565 --> 00:13:10,332
Sir Song Jiang.

159
00:13:10,332 --> 00:13:13,692
- Yes?
- Where are we headed?

160
00:13:15,249 --> 00:13:17,939
It shall be a surprise.

161
00:13:18,620 --> 00:13:20,620
Yes, sir.

162
00:13:20,620 --> 00:13:24,370
Is that a delicious fish?

163
00:13:25,600 --> 00:13:27,790
Depends on the cook.

164
00:13:29,335 --> 00:13:32,340
Her fever persists, and she is in pain.

165
00:13:32,340 --> 00:13:35,980
We cannot even converse any more.

166
00:13:35,980 --> 00:13:37,797
My wife, Chen Li, will die!

167
00:13:37,797 --> 00:13:39,600
Quiet.

168
00:13:39,600 --> 00:13:41,965
I am listening to her breathing.

169
00:13:41,965 --> 00:13:44,215
Zhu Gui.

170
00:13:44,215 --> 00:13:47,270
This man is the best doctor in the country.

171
00:13:47,270 --> 00:13:49,620
Let us leave the rest to him.

172
00:13:49,620 --> 00:13:50,996
Yes.

173
00:13:52,665 --> 00:13:55,030
You can save her, right?

174
00:13:55,030 --> 00:13:56,900
Her fever will die down.

175
00:13:56,900 --> 00:14:00,250
Xue Yong's medicine should take effect soon.

176
00:14:00,250 --> 00:14:01,515
What?

177
00:14:01,515 --> 00:14:04,905
Her fever is already less severe.

178
00:14:04,905 --> 00:14:07,085
Call out to her.

179
00:14:13,100 --> 00:14:14,730
Chen Li.

180
00:14:15,850 --> 00:14:17,660
Chen Li.

181
00:14:57,915 --> 00:15:00,690
My wife can speak again.

182
00:15:00,690 --> 00:15:02,588
Thank you for curing her.

183
00:15:02,588 --> 00:15:04,850
I have not cured her.

184
00:15:04,850 --> 00:15:07,810
I have only suppressed her fever and pain.

185
00:15:07,810 --> 00:15:10,215
She will likely manage to sit up as well.

186
00:15:10,215 --> 00:15:14,945
However, as time passes,
her fever will return.

187
00:15:17,365 --> 00:15:21,290
Though it is no trouble to quell her fever,

188
00:15:21,290 --> 00:15:27,300
she has a persisting sickness
in her bloodstream.

189
00:15:28,150 --> 00:15:30,530
A sickness, in her blood?

190
00:15:30,530 --> 00:15:35,630
There is currently no cure for such illness.

191
00:15:45,440 --> 00:15:47,410
Then Chen Li...

192
00:15:48,690 --> 00:15:51,380
Will my wife suffer again?

193
00:15:53,700 --> 00:16:00,050
No. I can abate her pain
until her final moments.

194
00:16:02,850 --> 00:16:04,660
An Dao Quan.

195
00:16:05,495 --> 00:16:09,610
Can you give this couple the time they need

196
00:16:09,610 --> 00:16:11,045
to converse and walk together,

197
00:16:11,045 --> 00:16:15,975
to smile and dine together,
like any other husband and wife?

198
00:16:19,480 --> 00:16:20,990
Yes, I can.

199
00:16:26,513 --> 00:16:28,153
Zhu Gui.

200
00:16:31,756 --> 00:16:38,926
How do you wish to spend your time
with your wife?

201
00:16:40,810 --> 00:16:42,970
I advise you to consider this carefully.

202
00:17:21,035 --> 00:17:24,190
Ma Gui and Shi Qian have sent their reports.

203
00:17:24,190 --> 00:17:28,990
It seems the Imperial Guard
has layers to their command.

204
00:17:29,805 --> 00:17:32,270
Intriguing. Tell me more.

205
00:17:32,270 --> 00:17:36,230
The emperor lies at the head of this nation.

206
00:17:36,230 --> 00:17:40,060
Yet he has no hand,
nor interest in political affairs.

207
00:17:40,060 --> 00:17:44,820
The one who truly rules this country,

208
00:17:44,820 --> 00:17:47,340
is the chancellor known as Cai Jing,

209
00:17:47,340 --> 00:17:52,195
and the Imperial Guard,
which controls our militia.

210
00:17:52,195 --> 00:17:57,455
In other words, Marshal Tong Guan.

211
00:17:58,305 --> 00:18:00,950
This is all nothing new.

212
00:18:00,950 --> 00:18:03,452
And yet true power lies elsewhere.

213
00:18:03,452 --> 00:18:05,052
What?

214
00:18:06,125 --> 00:18:11,270
To these men, their greatest obstacle

215
00:18:11,270 --> 00:18:14,650
is General Gao Qiu, of the Imperial Guard.

216
00:18:14,650 --> 00:18:17,835
Though he is an incompetent man,

217
00:18:17,835 --> 00:18:22,025
he excels at playing ball,
and currying the Emperor's favor.

218
00:18:22,700 --> 00:18:25,290
Officially,

219
00:18:26,020 --> 00:18:29,010
his position is below that of Tong Guan.

220
00:18:29,750 --> 00:18:33,220
Even so, he holds power,
as he is close to the Emperor.

221
00:18:35,955 --> 00:18:40,520
There is always a man like Gao Qiu
behind the downfall of a country.

222
00:18:40,520 --> 00:18:44,800
Most officials choose to obey Gao Qiu.

223
00:18:46,543 --> 00:18:53,470
Yet Cai Jing has a group of officials
who are at his command as well.

224
00:18:53,470 --> 00:18:55,700
This is the group I find to be suspicious.

225
00:18:55,700 --> 00:19:01,465
I had a spy tail one of these men.

226
00:19:01,465 --> 00:19:05,275
Only for this spy to commit suicide
the following day.

227
00:19:05,955 --> 00:19:09,210
Of course, he had no reason to die.

228
00:19:09,210 --> 00:19:13,400
So I sent another spy,

229
00:19:13,400 --> 00:19:17,000
for him to ultimately meet the same fate.

230
00:19:19,745 --> 00:19:25,580
The official I had them tail, was named...

231
00:19:25,580 --> 00:19:27,250
Li Fu.

232
00:19:28,825 --> 00:19:32,480
The man Lin Chong suspected.

233
00:19:32,480 --> 00:19:34,430
Indeed.

234
00:19:41,020 --> 00:19:42,590
Li Fu.

235
00:19:43,225 --> 00:19:48,230
He killed two of my men,
and covered it up as a suicide.

236
00:19:48,230 --> 00:19:51,070
He is no ordinary civil servant.

237
00:19:51,070 --> 00:19:54,344
Then he is part of an organization.

238
00:19:54,344 --> 00:19:56,440
What else do you know?

239
00:19:56,440 --> 00:20:00,370
I did not have Ma Gui
investigate any further.

240
00:20:00,370 --> 00:20:02,480
Song Jiang.

241
00:20:02,480 --> 00:20:04,940
Ma Gui's husband died for your sake.

242
00:20:04,940 --> 00:20:08,505
Do you keep her as a retainer out of pity?

243
00:20:08,505 --> 00:20:10,225
I know, Chao Gai.

244
00:20:10,980 --> 00:20:15,790
I will have Ma Gui retire in the coming days.

245
00:20:16,675 --> 00:20:23,520
If we are against
an intelligence organization of sorts,

246
00:20:23,520 --> 00:20:26,130
they will be more troublesome
than the Imperial Guard.

247
00:20:32,270 --> 00:20:35,040
Do you have some plan to combat this?

248
00:20:43,495 --> 00:20:46,650
We shall organize the Zhishi Squadron.

249
00:20:46,650 --> 00:20:48,410
The Zhishi Squadron?

250
00:20:49,455 --> 00:20:55,020
The covert squad utilized by the Wu Dynasty
of the Three Kingdoms,

251
00:20:55,020 --> 00:20:59,775
to overcome all obstacles,
and sneak behind enemy camps?

252
00:20:59,775 --> 00:21:05,940
Yes. They will infiltrate the enemy base,
and attack from within.

253
00:21:05,940 --> 00:21:10,270
It is not an army,
reliant on the strength of one man.

254
00:21:10,270 --> 00:21:13,945
But a unit, that works in harmony.

255
00:21:13,945 --> 00:21:17,985
Yes, we shall revive their legend once more.

256
00:21:18,900 --> 00:21:22,170
They will prove useful
in smuggling salt as well.

257
00:21:23,190 --> 00:21:25,240
Song Jiang.

258
00:21:26,230 --> 00:21:32,540
Do you know a man
who could lead such a covert group?

259
00:21:37,585 --> 00:21:40,690
A man who is not flashy, but discreet.

260
00:21:40,690 --> 00:21:45,520
Who is strong, and has fresh ideas.

261
00:21:45,520 --> 00:21:47,715
A man who can operate in secrecy, perhaps?

262
00:21:47,715 --> 00:21:50,985
Yes. That, exactly.

263
00:22:04,950 --> 00:22:07,630
What a strange coincidence indeed.

264
00:22:09,820 --> 00:22:11,750
What is this?

265
00:22:12,995 --> 00:22:17,480
It is the last correspondence from Yan Xin.

266
00:22:17,480 --> 00:22:20,080
I had him searching for kindred spirits,

267
00:22:20,080 --> 00:22:23,630
when he found a man
by the name of "Gongsun Sheng".

268
00:22:23,630 --> 00:22:29,505
He is a master of disguise,
who has honed all five of his senses.

269
00:22:29,505 --> 00:22:35,605
I believe he could lead a covert unit
like the Zhishi Squadron.

270
00:22:36,320 --> 00:22:39,040
However, there is just one problem.

271
00:22:40,980 --> 00:22:44,810
What it is? Keep no secrets, Song Jiang.

272
00:22:49,076 --> 00:22:51,386
He, too, is imprisoned.

273
00:22:55,745 --> 00:22:59,080
He has been locked up for two years now.

274
00:22:59,080 --> 00:23:03,275
Another jailbreak, is it?

275
00:23:03,275 --> 00:23:10,315
All the capable men in this country
are either imprisoned, or killed.

276
00:23:22,040 --> 00:23:25,000
I will bring to you...

277
00:23:26,510 --> 00:23:28,380
this so-called master of disguise.

278
00:23:39,560 --> 00:23:41,500
Yan Xin.

279
00:23:43,020 --> 00:23:48,340
Even after death, you continue to aid me.

280
00:24:11,530 --> 00:24:19,200
Watching them, it feels as though
they will manage to walk on forever.

281
00:24:20,030 --> 00:24:22,465
Indeed, it does.

282
00:24:22,465 --> 00:24:24,310
Unfortunately,

283
00:24:24,310 --> 00:24:28,190
we have only given her
a higher dose of medicine today.

284
00:24:28,190 --> 00:24:30,835
Chen Li insisted.

285
00:24:30,835 --> 00:24:35,145
The consequence being,
she will be bedridden tomorrow.

286
00:24:37,225 --> 00:24:39,980
I don't think she minds.

287
00:24:39,980 --> 00:24:42,250
So long as she can have this moment.

288
00:24:44,135 --> 00:24:46,190
Po Xi.

289
00:24:46,190 --> 00:24:51,425
Can you assist in caring for Chen Li?

290
00:24:51,425 --> 00:24:55,065
I believe she will feel relieved
having a fellow woman at her side.

291
00:24:55,850 --> 00:24:57,620
I suppose she would.

292
00:24:58,490 --> 00:25:01,250
Yes, I shall assist her.

293
00:25:26,160 --> 00:25:29,000
The fortress at Liangshan Marsh, is it?

294
00:25:31,705 --> 00:25:35,360
Song Jiang, I see you are no ordinary clerk.

295
00:25:35,360 --> 00:25:40,380
You wish to use my connections
to seize that very fortress.

296
00:25:41,125 --> 00:25:42,660
Zhu Gui...

297
00:25:42,660 --> 00:25:45,350
There lives a monster within that fortress.

298
00:25:45,350 --> 00:25:48,190
A monster, known as "authority".

299
00:25:48,190 --> 00:25:51,060
No matter what noble ambitions
an individual may have,

300
00:25:51,060 --> 00:25:56,230
that monster will infect you with greed.

301
00:25:56,230 --> 00:25:58,250
Like it did to Wang Lun.

302
00:26:00,625 --> 00:26:03,350
I will not fall trap to this monster.

303
00:26:03,350 --> 00:26:05,435
Zhu Gui, I am...

304
00:26:05,435 --> 00:26:09,315
It seems I cannot stop you, no?

305
00:26:12,360 --> 00:26:14,240
I understand.

306
00:26:16,730 --> 00:26:20,880
I will make the necessary preparations.

307
00:26:41,005 --> 00:26:43,560
I was dreaming, dear.

308
00:26:43,560 --> 00:26:46,068
What occurred in your dream?

309
00:26:46,068 --> 00:26:48,665
Strangely enough,
I was witnessing this exact view,

310
00:26:48,665 --> 00:26:52,075
where you all were at my side when I awoke.

311
00:26:54,635 --> 00:26:57,560
Perhaps I am still dreaming?

312
00:26:57,560 --> 00:26:59,055
No.

313
00:26:59,055 --> 00:27:02,895
Chen Li, this is no dream.

314
00:27:20,160 --> 00:27:22,830
I long for my family.

315
00:27:26,460 --> 00:27:28,000
Your family?

316
00:27:28,940 --> 00:27:35,580
I have a father, Song Ying,
and a younger brother, Song Qing.

317
00:27:36,415 --> 00:27:39,480
Watching Zhu Gui and his wife today

318
00:27:39,480 --> 00:27:44,760
had me ponder happiness once more.

319
00:27:46,400 --> 00:27:50,660
Do you ever miss your father?

320
00:27:51,675 --> 00:27:53,580
Sometimes.

321
00:27:53,580 --> 00:27:55,200
I see.

322
00:27:56,665 --> 00:27:59,750
Your father, Yan Xin,

323
00:27:59,750 --> 00:28:05,980
was an incredibly capable man.

324
00:28:07,320 --> 00:28:12,460
And now you and your mother
both work as my subordinates.

325
00:28:13,650 --> 00:28:19,420
I owe quite a bit to your family.

326
00:28:23,790 --> 00:28:28,330
What sort of work does my mother do for you?

327
00:28:32,100 --> 00:28:33,620
Po Xi.

328
00:28:34,377 --> 00:28:37,020
Leave us.

329
00:28:37,020 --> 00:28:39,160
- Mother?
- Po Xi.

330
00:28:46,490 --> 00:28:48,000
Yes, Mother.

331
00:29:00,665 --> 00:29:02,740
Sir Song Jiang.

332
00:29:02,740 --> 00:29:07,380
Why have you removed me as your spy?

333
00:29:08,045 --> 00:29:11,920
Since the day my husband passed,

334
00:29:11,920 --> 00:29:15,270
I have taken up his mantle as your spy.

335
00:29:15,270 --> 00:29:17,480
Ma Gui.

336
00:29:17,480 --> 00:29:19,330
Listen well.

337
00:29:20,810 --> 00:29:25,370
These missions are to become quite perilous.

338
00:29:26,410 --> 00:29:31,750
As Po Xi's mother,
I cannot endanger you any further.

339
00:29:38,737 --> 00:29:43,560
I want you to find happiness,
as any ordinary woman would.

340
00:29:43,560 --> 00:29:45,830
An ordinary woman?

341
00:29:47,785 --> 00:29:50,980
After the death of my parents as a child,

342
00:29:50,980 --> 00:29:54,240
I was raised to be a spy.

343
00:29:55,020 --> 00:29:57,420
You think I can become an "ordinary" woman?

344
00:29:58,260 --> 00:30:04,430
I do not know how else to live my life.

345
00:30:06,807 --> 00:30:08,397
Ma Gui.

346
00:30:25,243 --> 00:30:27,113
Dark in here, is it not?

347
00:30:32,100 --> 00:30:34,590
You must be Gongsun Sheng.

348
00:30:43,330 --> 00:30:47,460
Tell me, have you injured your eyes?

349
00:30:48,910 --> 00:30:52,720
I apologize for greeting you
with my eyes shut.

350
00:30:53,812 --> 00:30:58,469
They are still sensitive,
as I had been deprived of any light

351
00:30:58,469 --> 00:31:01,069
for two years now.

352
00:31:03,360 --> 00:31:09,040
I hope to recover my sight by moonlight.

353
00:31:13,040 --> 00:31:16,630
Your long trial has now come to an end.

354
00:31:17,690 --> 00:31:19,630
Chao Gai.
[Gongsun Sheng, Former Prisoner]

355
00:31:20,705 --> 00:31:22,790
Why have you rescued me?

356
00:31:22,790 --> 00:31:29,982
You excel in stealth, or so I hear.

357
00:31:34,850 --> 00:31:38,760
As such, we hope
you will lead a particular unit for us.

358
00:31:39,690 --> 00:31:42,410
What sort of unit, if I may ask?

359
00:31:45,440 --> 00:31:47,210
A covert unit, the Zhishi Squadron.

360
00:31:57,080 --> 00:32:01,000
Do tell me more.

361
00:32:10,375 --> 00:32:15,250
Even we do not know what lies ahead.

362
00:32:15,250 --> 00:32:17,725
Please, travel with utmost caution.

363
00:32:17,725 --> 00:32:19,745
Yes, sir.

364
00:32:19,745 --> 00:32:22,280
Wang Lun took that fortress as his home

365
00:32:22,280 --> 00:32:26,095
as he, too, held grievances
towards this nation.

366
00:32:26,095 --> 00:32:28,700
His goals were once the same as ours.

367
00:32:28,700 --> 00:32:34,600
Yet some say he has regressed
to a common bandit.

368
00:32:34,600 --> 00:32:37,249
I shall seek the truth behind his ambitions.

369
00:32:37,249 --> 00:32:42,358
We will maintain communications
through Xue Yong.

370
00:32:42,358 --> 00:32:46,713
Though your conversations
may be monitored within,

371
00:32:46,713 --> 00:32:51,023
Xue Yong can leave the fortress
under the guise of foraging herbs.

372
00:32:51,900 --> 00:32:54,440
He is a reassuring ally to have.

373
00:32:54,440 --> 00:32:56,000
Song Jiang, Chao Gai.

374
00:32:58,020 --> 00:33:00,540
We shall briefly part ways here.

375
00:33:12,310 --> 00:33:13,790
We shall set off.

376
00:33:38,210 --> 00:33:39,790
Zhu Gui.

377
00:33:40,940 --> 00:33:43,170
Do you not feel an immense sorrow?

378
00:33:44,150 --> 00:33:46,370
You must be referring to Chen Li's fate.

379
00:33:47,319 --> 00:33:49,254
I...

380
00:33:49,254 --> 00:33:52,679
No, we are happy now.

381
00:33:55,015 --> 00:33:57,520
I was once determined to stay far away

382
00:33:57,520 --> 00:34:00,540
from the love between a man and woman.

383
00:34:01,190 --> 00:34:03,010
Even so...

384
00:34:04,230 --> 00:34:08,790
When I see you and your wife,
my determination wavers.

385
00:34:10,190 --> 00:34:14,480
It seems I had misunderstood you, Lin Chong.

386
00:34:14,480 --> 00:34:20,250
I once assumed the Panther Head
knew only aggression in his heart.

387
00:34:40,400 --> 00:34:41,950
Chao Gai.

388
00:34:43,285 --> 00:34:46,350
If I one day fall to greed,

389
00:34:46,350 --> 00:34:49,630
and become a mere bandit,

390
00:34:52,440 --> 00:34:54,790
I ask that you strike me down.

391
00:34:57,570 --> 00:34:58,960
Of course.

392
00:35:01,520 --> 00:35:05,410
I ask that you do the same,
if I begin walking a similar path.

393
00:35:17,650 --> 00:35:19,750
We are almost there.

394
00:36:36,321 --> 00:36:39,850
Zhu Gui, thank you for your guidance.

395
00:36:39,850 --> 00:36:42,925
No, I must thank you, Lin Chong.

396
00:36:42,925 --> 00:36:49,100
You are the reason Chen Li smiles again.

397
00:36:49,100 --> 00:36:50,660
I wish you luck.

398
00:36:55,610 --> 00:36:57,540
Take care.

399
00:36:59,415 --> 00:37:02,190
You worry for me?

400
00:37:02,190 --> 00:37:06,410
If you do not return alive,
Song Jiang will mourn.

401
00:37:07,730 --> 00:37:11,720
Come, I will escort you to our fortress.

402
00:37:16,850 --> 00:37:18,200
Let us set off.

403
00:37:53,020 --> 00:37:55,540
We shall take your spear.

404
00:37:56,270 --> 00:37:59,020
- My spear?
- It is the law here.

405
00:38:03,000 --> 00:38:04,660
Your sword as well.

406
00:38:12,750 --> 00:38:14,250
Enter.

407
00:38:41,780 --> 00:38:45,110
[Du Qian, Second in command]
[Song Wan, Third in command]

408
00:38:56,205 --> 00:38:58,600
Lin Chong.

409
00:38:58,600 --> 00:39:00,615
An Dao Quan.

410
00:39:00,615 --> 00:39:02,435
Xue Yong.

411
00:39:06,722 --> 00:39:09,540
I am Wang Lun.
[Wang Lun, Leader of Liangshan Marsh]

412
00:39:09,540 --> 00:39:11,470
The leader of Liangshan Marsh.

413
00:39:17,020 --> 00:39:19,130
Lin Chong.

414
00:39:20,690 --> 00:39:24,370
There are plenty here
who boast their spearmanship.

415
00:39:25,150 --> 00:39:28,000
How about a spar, as a show of greeting?

416
00:39:29,630 --> 00:39:33,950
My apprentices would love to test themselves.

417
00:39:35,820 --> 00:39:37,790
What do you say, Lin Chong?

418
00:39:39,810 --> 00:39:44,410
Fine. Then may I have a pole?

419
00:39:45,665 --> 00:39:48,350
Lin Chong.

420
00:39:48,350 --> 00:39:51,820
This is not the Imperial Guard.

421
00:39:51,820 --> 00:39:56,850
You shall spar with a spear.

422
00:39:56,850 --> 00:40:01,770
I do not wish to kill as a greeting.

423
00:40:01,770 --> 00:40:03,980
Your men must stay alive.

424
00:40:03,980 --> 00:40:05,490
Are you frightened, Lin Chong?

425
00:40:05,490 --> 00:40:07,200
Master Hong.

426
00:40:07,200 --> 00:40:11,810
Look at how the Imperial Guard has fallen.

427
00:40:11,810 --> 00:40:13,810
You are being disrespectful.

428
00:40:13,810 --> 00:40:16,290
My apologies.

429
00:40:16,290 --> 00:40:19,375
He had simply been stunned silent,

430
00:40:19,375 --> 00:40:21,485
I felt it necessary to fill the air.

431
00:40:24,030 --> 00:40:25,870
Fine.

432
00:40:26,860 --> 00:40:28,970
I shall take them all at once.

433
00:40:36,205 --> 00:40:37,950
An Dao Quan.

434
00:40:37,950 --> 00:40:40,650
I tried to keep their bones intact.

435
00:40:40,650 --> 00:40:43,193
I would like a proper clinic.

436
00:40:43,193 --> 00:40:47,413
If your men are so fragile,
I will need the space to treat them.

437
00:41:02,190 --> 00:41:08,160
You truly are the greatest spearman
in the nation, Lin Chong.

438
00:41:15,880 --> 00:41:18,095
Lin Chong.

439
00:41:18,095 --> 00:41:21,440
How goes the clinic?

440
00:41:21,440 --> 00:41:25,620
An Dao Quan and Xue Yong
are steadily furnishing it.

441
00:41:27,654 --> 00:41:32,169
Once we have a clinic,
we need not fear any illnesses.

442
00:41:32,169 --> 00:41:33,819
Indeed.

443
00:41:34,995 --> 00:41:38,370
Some illnesses cannot be cured.

444
00:41:38,370 --> 00:41:40,239
What?

445
00:41:40,239 --> 00:41:43,299
Zhu Gui's wife, she is...

446
00:41:46,535 --> 00:41:49,070
Ah, Zhu Gui's wife.

447
00:41:49,070 --> 00:41:51,315
Does he wish to join our cause?

448
00:41:51,315 --> 00:41:53,520
Du Qian.

449
00:41:53,520 --> 00:41:55,450
Pardon my brazenness, sir.

450
00:41:56,855 --> 00:41:59,750
Lin Chong, an envoy for the Imperial Guard

451
00:41:59,750 --> 00:42:03,390
will be passing this area
in three days' time.

452
00:42:03,390 --> 00:42:04,810
An envoy?

453
00:42:04,810 --> 00:42:07,730
They are soldiers given special orders

454
00:42:07,730 --> 00:42:11,600
to search for corrupt local officials
in exchange for bribery.

455
00:42:11,600 --> 00:42:13,555
This makes the role a coveted one.

456
00:42:13,555 --> 00:42:17,950
However, this envoy is not unlike the others.

457
00:42:17,950 --> 00:42:21,295
They say he accepts no bribes.

458
00:42:21,295 --> 00:42:22,870
I see.

459
00:42:22,870 --> 00:42:28,005
What's more,
it seems he is aiming for this fortress.

460
00:42:28,005 --> 00:42:30,975
Then my role is simple.

461
00:42:32,159 --> 00:42:34,470
I will merely do away with him.

462
00:42:44,915 --> 00:42:47,730
You must not kill the envoy.

463
00:42:47,730 --> 00:42:49,520
What?

464
00:42:49,520 --> 00:42:54,045
That envoy is a man named Yang Zhi,
descendant of Yang Ye.

465
00:42:54,045 --> 00:42:58,685
Song Jiang hopes to recruit him to our cause.

466
00:42:59,790 --> 00:43:01,960
Is he capable in battle?

467
00:43:02,785 --> 00:43:05,900
So I hear.

468
00:43:05,900 --> 00:43:11,620
He also wields the famous
"Splitting Hairs Blade".

469
00:43:11,620 --> 00:43:14,580
So I must defeat this man,
without taking his life?

470
00:43:16,986 --> 00:43:18,976
You ask for the impossible.

471
00:43:19,690 --> 00:43:22,330
I am certain you can figure something out.

472
00:43:25,160 --> 00:43:27,250
That, I wonder.

473
00:43:32,060 --> 00:43:33,690
You are in time.

474
00:43:37,825 --> 00:43:39,210
A bandit?

475
00:43:39,210 --> 00:43:43,040
No. I am merely a spearman,
here to test my skills.

476
00:43:43,715 --> 00:43:48,370
You look to be quite skilled yourself.

477
00:43:48,370 --> 00:43:50,480
I am known as Yang Zhi.

478
00:43:50,480 --> 00:43:54,180
You wish to duel, knowing I am an envoy?

479
00:43:54,180 --> 00:43:57,770
Yang Zhi, the Blue-faced Beast.

480
00:43:57,770 --> 00:43:59,520
That is right.

481
00:43:59,520 --> 00:44:06,190
Then is that the Splitting Hairs Blade?

482
00:44:06,190 --> 00:44:08,350
You are aware of my blade?

483
00:44:08,350 --> 00:44:11,020
Though spears are my specialty,

484
00:44:11,020 --> 00:44:15,535
I do not mind dueling with a sword.

485
00:44:15,535 --> 00:44:20,065
Let us each wield whatever we please.

486
00:44:48,430 --> 00:44:51,050
Do not kill him, Lin Chong.

487
00:44:51,050 --> 00:44:54,180
Neither man must die.

488
00:45:26,870 --> 00:45:29,540
Why keep your Splitting Hairs Blade sheathed?

489
00:45:31,305 --> 00:45:36,177
My Splitting Hairs Blade is a noble sword,
used to protect our nation.

490
00:45:36,177 --> 00:45:41,797
I would never taint it with a bandit's blood.

491
00:45:46,165 --> 00:45:48,520
Lin Chong is amazing.

492
00:45:48,520 --> 00:45:50,350
Don't you agree, Du Qian?

493
00:45:50,350 --> 00:45:52,280
Indeed.

494
00:45:52,280 --> 00:45:54,625
I do not wish for either man to die.

495
00:45:54,625 --> 00:45:57,825
They fight an honorable duel.

496
00:45:58,467 --> 00:46:01,057
That is a dangerous thought to have.

497
00:46:31,765 --> 00:46:33,940
The duel is over.

498
00:46:33,940 --> 00:46:35,410
Lin Chong!

499
00:46:36,465 --> 00:46:38,850
Why do you hesitate?

500
00:46:38,850 --> 00:46:41,080
Because I do not wish to kill you.

501
00:46:41,840 --> 00:46:44,010
That is what our duel has proven.

502
00:46:44,795 --> 00:46:46,536
Did you have someone aiding you?

503
00:46:46,536 --> 00:46:50,956
No. I simply hoped to see more of your sword.

504
00:46:51,940 --> 00:46:53,720
That is all.

505
00:46:55,524 --> 00:46:57,368
No, it cannot be...

506
00:46:58,747 --> 00:47:00,599
Are you Lin Chong?

507
00:47:02,415 --> 00:47:04,570
I wonder.

508
00:47:04,570 --> 00:47:08,230
Your spearmanship speaks for itself.

509
00:47:08,230 --> 00:47:11,585
Believe what you wish.

510
00:47:11,585 --> 00:47:13,145
Kill me!

511
00:47:14,165 --> 00:47:16,940
Do not test me, Yang Zhi!

512
00:47:16,940 --> 00:47:20,775
Why use such an honorable blade
for the Imperial Guard,

513
00:47:20,775 --> 00:47:23,605
and not for our people?

514
00:47:26,385 --> 00:47:28,900
I am but a mere foot soldier.

515
00:47:28,900 --> 00:47:30,810
If I am ordered to fight, I fight.

516
00:47:30,810 --> 00:47:32,650
If I suffer defeat, then I perish.

517
00:47:32,650 --> 00:47:34,150
That is all.

518
00:47:34,150 --> 00:47:39,150
Does our imperial court now
warrant such fighting?

519
00:47:39,150 --> 00:47:42,385
Our imperial court,

520
00:47:42,385 --> 00:47:44,865
that is practically manipulated by Gao Qiu?

521
00:47:46,715 --> 00:47:50,560
Defect, like I have.

522
00:47:50,560 --> 00:47:52,225
Leave, and you will find your path!

523
00:47:52,225 --> 00:47:53,815
Enough!

524
00:47:54,675 --> 00:47:58,560
Pierce my chest with that spear of yours!

525
00:47:58,560 --> 00:48:03,750
I will not wield my spear in such a manner.

526
00:48:09,080 --> 00:48:14,630
Return to the Imperial Guard,
and take a good look at your masters.

527
00:48:16,120 --> 00:48:19,950
If then, you still wish to die at my spear,

528
00:48:21,440 --> 00:48:23,660
return here, where we stand.

529
00:48:49,860 --> 00:48:52,660
He won the duel, and chased off the envoy.

530
00:48:55,960 --> 00:49:00,630
Why spare him, Lin Chong?

531
00:49:08,850 --> 00:49:12,160
Is he a dog of the Imperial Guard?

532
00:49:28,690 --> 00:49:31,020
Splendid battling, Lin Chong.

533
00:49:32,600 --> 00:49:37,250
But why did you not
deliver the finishing blow?

534
00:49:38,656 --> 00:49:44,666
It would be a waste
to lose a commander of his caliber.

535
00:49:46,190 --> 00:49:48,080
I see.

536
00:49:49,900 --> 00:49:51,960
Tonight, we will celebrate.

537
00:50:01,875 --> 00:50:06,060
Those in the Imperial Guard
acknowledged your superiority

538
00:50:06,060 --> 00:50:10,400
as an ancestor of Yang Ye.

539
00:50:10,400 --> 00:50:14,835
Yet you spent your time
aimlessly wandering the nation.

540
00:50:14,835 --> 00:50:18,085
I surveyed our lands thoroughly, sir.

541
00:50:18,085 --> 00:50:21,270
Did you enjoy your rendezvous
with those bandits?

542
00:50:21,270 --> 00:50:22,970
I did no such thing!

543
00:50:24,885 --> 00:50:28,960
You have proven your incompetence

544
00:50:28,960 --> 00:50:32,965
despite being an envoy of my army.

545
00:50:32,965 --> 00:50:37,145
We do not need men like you
in the Imperial Guard.

546
00:50:39,040 --> 00:50:42,660
Prove yourself useful in the Qingzhou army.

547
00:50:44,169 --> 00:50:47,784
As you wish, General.

548
00:50:47,784 --> 00:50:49,584
Stand down!

549
00:51:05,345 --> 00:51:09,156
<i>I will not wield my spear in such a manner.</i>

550
00:51:09,156 --> 00:51:15,086
<i>Return to the Imperial Guard,
and take a good look at your masters.</i>

551
00:52:10,210 --> 00:52:13,080
Men, prepare your cups!

552
00:52:14,125 --> 00:52:17,790
To Lin Chong's victory. Cheers!

553
00:52:17,790 --> 00:52:20,875
Cheers.

554
00:52:20,875 --> 00:52:23,275
Drink up!

555
00:52:26,625 --> 00:52:29,960
Bring the alcohol and food!

556
00:52:29,960 --> 00:52:31,625
Tonight, we drink till dawn.

557
00:52:31,625 --> 00:52:33,825
Bring the alcohol in troves!

558
00:53:50,980 --> 00:53:53,440
Lin Chong!

559
00:53:53,440 --> 00:53:55,040
Lin Chong!

560
00:53:57,800 --> 00:53:59,580
Lin Chong!

561
00:54:02,965 --> 00:54:04,300
Lin Chong!

562
00:54:04,300 --> 00:54:05,935
Lin Chong!

563
00:54:05,935 --> 00:54:08,435
Lin Chong! Are you alright?

564
00:54:34,415 --> 00:54:37,100
Show me your tenacity.

565
00:54:37,100 --> 00:54:40,860
A tiger-slaying hero
has practically fallen.

566
00:54:40,860 --> 00:54:42,480
I cannot betray my country.

567
00:54:42,480 --> 00:54:44,690
My ancestry prevents me from doing so.

568
00:54:44,690 --> 00:54:46,900
You must know quite the tactician.

569
00:54:46,900 --> 00:54:51,250
This will not end lightly for you.

570
00:54:51,250 --> 00:54:52,474
Kill him.

571
00:54:52,474 --> 00:54:54,650
Do you fear Wang Lun's scrutiny?

572
00:54:54,650 --> 00:54:56,560
What I fear is suspecting my fellow men.

573
00:54:56,560 --> 00:54:58,730
4,000 soldiers
have been deployed from Beijing.

574
00:54:58,730 --> 00:55:00,940
They are after your neck, Sir Chao Gai.

575
00:55:00,940 --> 00:55:03,210
You will be killed.

576
00:55:03,210 --> 00:55:05,425
There is no gamble I cannot win.

577
00:55:05,425 --> 00:55:07,115
Song Jiang.

578
00:55:07,910 --> 00:55:10,250
Believe in me!

579
00:56:54,650 --> 00:57:00,520
[Episode 4 - FIN]

